, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px;"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">5. SSL with Let‚Äôs Encrypt (for local domain testing)</span></strong></h4><p style="background-color: #071a29; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">You can use </span><code style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: source-code-pro, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Courier New", monospace;">mkcert</code><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;"> or local certificates. For public SSL, you‚Äôd still need a domain and port forwarding.</span></p><hr style="background-color: #071a29; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji"; font-size: 14px;" /><h3 style="background-color: #071a29; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Segoe UI Symbol", "Noto Color Emoji";"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space-collapse: preserve;">FOR PUBLIC HOSTING VIA WSL</span></strong></h3><p style="background-color: #071a29; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "Noto Sans", sans-serif, "Apple Color Emoji", "Segoe UI Emoji", "Seg